'''Durbaan''', '''Durmaan''' ({{lang-en|''drum''}}; {{lang-ar|طبلة}}) waa qalab ka samaysan [[geed|alwaaxyo]] iyo [[harag]] la isku giijiyay kaasi oo la garaaco (tumo) si uu u sameeyo [[cod|shanqadha cod]] [[muusig]]. Durbaanku wuxu ka mid yahay qalabka ugu da'da weyn ee dadku isticmaali jireen tan iyo horaantii ilbaxnimada.

=Faalo=


[[File:TalkingDrum.jpg|thumb|right|nooc ka mid ah durmaanka.]]

Durbaanku wuxuu ka samaysan yahay dahaar (inta ugu badan harag) lagu duubay weel adag (inta badan geed la qoray) kaasi oo lagu garaaco hal ama labo ulood ama gacmaha si uu u sameeyo shanqadh hadba nooca loo garaaco ku xidhan.<ref>{{cite book|title=Grove Dictionary of Music and Musicians|The New Grove Encyclopædia of Music and Musicians]]|edition=2nd|first=George|last=Grove|authorlink=George Grove|editor=Stanley Sadie]]|date=January 2001|publisher=Grove's Dictionaries of Music|pages=Volume 5, pp638–649|isbn=1-56159-239-0}}</ref> Sida badan durbaanka Waxaa garaaca hal qof kaasi oo isticmaalaya gacmaha ama ulo, Sidoo kale Waxaa jirta in tiro badab oo durmaano ah hal mar la wada garaaco si ay u sameeyaan shanqadh aad u balaadhan.

=Isticmaalka=
Ujeedada durbaanka loo isticmaalo waxay ku xidhan tahay dadka, deegaanka iyo dhaqanka. Laakiin guud ahaan Waxaa loo isticmaalaa in uu qurxiyo [[cod]], [[hees]], [[gabay]], [[geeraar]], [[ciyaar]] iyo wixii la mid ah. Tusaale ahaan, deegaanada dadka [[Soomaalida]] ku nool yihiin waxaa durmaanka la isticmaalaa wakhtiyada dabaaldega, xafladaha, arooska iyo wixii la mid ah.<ref>{{Cite news
